title: Export multiple files with same file name under different directories to zip file fails.
description:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Export multiple files with the same name ('foo.txt') under different directories to a zip file. 

OB:
EB: The zip file fails to store multiple files with the same name ('foo.txt') under different directories.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Create two different directories in the project. 
2. Rename both files in each directory to 'foo.txt'.
3. Export both directories to a zip file.
4. Observe the behavior of the zip file storage.
